    rating: 5,
    title: 'Amazing',
    text: 'Met Belinda on the beach , she recommended the best day to go ( weather wise) chose the 8 hour trip which I highly recommend. We were a family of 2 adults and 2 kids age 9 and 5 . Our captain and co host was robin and Emily and they were both amazing and couldn’t do enough for us 😊 . The trip was was of our best ever , beautiful waterfalls , feeding monkeys , up close to dolphins and I mentioned I liked fishing before so they put a rod on the boat and we caught fish . Stopped off at a deserted lighthouse with stunning views , my son got to drive the boat which he loved , few Mauritian  coffee 😉 too . Finished off on a private beach eating fresh lobster / fish chicken , wine . Amazing day . Don’t miss out if your heading to Mauritius, go see Belinda 👌🏽👌🏽 \n\nThanks once again 😘😘',
