    source: 'TripAdvisor',
    rating: 5,
    title: 'Very Professional',
    text: 'We used this company to do 2 tours of the island ( south and north ) and no question about it a great company to use if you are holidaying here. They provide airport transfers as well way below the price asked at our hotel. Contact is easy and I had to use WhatsApp as my emails were playing up . Each tour lasted about 5/6 hours and cost 2200 rupees (about £48 ) Both drivers were very pleasant and nothing was too much trouble. Tell them what you are interested in and they will show you what the island has to offer. You can squeeze in up to 4 persons for that price and the cost will only inflate if you want to visit a paid attraction. Ask for Kadir as he is very well mannered , easy to understand and more than happy to enjoy your time out. Nagesh was our contact on +23057908414 and he responded very quickly to our enquiries',
