    text: 'THIS COMPANY MADE OUR MAURITIUS VISIT SOOO ENJOYABLE!  We booked several services from this company … 2 airport transfers and 6 different tours.  Geerja in the office was quick to respond to all inquiries.  Robert, our driver, was a very good driver and ensured that we were comfortable, was always timely, and assisted us with park entries etc.  I did a lot of comparative shopping with other companies and found that Belle Mare was the best value.  Go to their website, which has many more activities listed than the few that were listed on TripAdvisor or Viator or Getmyguide.  You can book directly with the company.  You pay on the day of the activity and can cancel your reservation for no penalty if done two days prior to the activity.',
