    text: 'We used Belle Mare tours after reading the excellent reviews on Tripadvisor. Our contact person was Noorani who was very helpful. His ’can do ’ attitude and customer focus does him and his company great credit. First was the speedboat tour to Blue Bay and back which was a fantastic day out for an excellent price. Note however that when it comes to snorkelling in Blue Bay you need your own snorkelling equipment although life jackets were provided if wanted. This wasn’t clear from their website and it could be helpful if they listed what you need to bring. We then rented a brand new small car from them for a reasonable price with free hotel delivery and pick up from Longbeach hotel. Everything went very smoothly with on time hotel pick ups, car delivery etc. Payment by credit card was no problem.',
